Django Formset

Django formset is a way to handle many forms of the same type in the same template

This code help us to build dynamic formsets in the template using
Vanilla JavaScript

what mean dynamic formsets?

- we can add new form
- we can delete form
in one second.

only applying

form = document.querySelector('form-content')
f = new Formset(form)
f.create()

and the formset is ready.